This is the Perl distribution Module-Install-ReadmeMarkdownFromPod.

## Installation

Module-Install-ReadmeMarkdownFromPod installation is straightforward. If your
CPAN shell is set up, you should just be able to do

    % cpan Module::Install::ReadmeMarkdownFromPod

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

## Documentation

Module-Install-ReadmeMarkdownFromPod documentation is available as in POD. So
you can do:

    % perldoc Module::Install::ReadmeMarkdownFromPod

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

